<template meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" style="margin: 0; overflow: hidden;">
    <a-scene
      vr-mode-ui="enabled: false"
      embedded
      arjs="sourceType: webcam; debugUIEnabled: false;"
    >
      <a-text
        value="Picture."
        look-at="[gps-camera]"
        scale="100 90 60"
        gps-entity-place="latitude: 55.645811926975384; longitude: 37.6493525505066;"
      ></a-text>
      <a-camera gps-camera rotation-reader> </a-camera>
    </a-scene>
</template>
<script>
  import "../ar/aframe.min.js";
  import "..ar/aframe-look-at-component.min.js";
  import "../ar/aframe-ar-nft.js";
</script>
